						               													<description>From the publisher's website:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Apocalypse is here!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The dead of the Earth have risen, and now they roam the land seeking living beings to feed upon. Powerful undead such as vampires and ghouls command legions of flesh-hungry zombies in chilling, inhuman war bands. Small pockets of resistance remain as humans wage a desperate battle for survival in a world where the waters have turned to blood and the sky is night everlasting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Final Days is a complete boxed miniatures combat game where players command human freedom fighters or undead hordes in Earth's final battle! The combat system uses standard playing cards to determine the outcome of actions, and takes just minutes to learn. Play seamlessly with just two players or a group of eight or more! Everything you need to set up and play this fast-paced, hard-action game is included, and you can be up and  running in no time. This boxed set includes Twenty-Five 25mm metal figures (8 different brand-new sculpts) to recreate your intense tabletop battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;So grab your shotgun and bar the doors. The dead are coming and nobody is there to rescue you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Final Days is a skirmish-level miniatures game that uses a standard deck of playing cards, with jokers, as its randomizer.  Each figure has three attributes that determine how many cards it draws during combat, as well as determining how much damage the figure can take.  As a figure takes damage, his combat effectiveness decreases.  The game can be played with any number of players, and lasts on average 1 to 2 hours.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Box Contents&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rulebook&amp;#10;Scenario and Accessory Book&amp;#10;2 Double-sided B&amp;amp;W maps&amp;#10;Templates of burned-out cars, desks, dumpsters&amp;#10;2 Combat Trackers&amp;#10;Equipment counters&amp;#10;25 white metal miniatures:&amp;#10;Demon&amp;#10;Vampire&amp;#10;2 Ghouls&amp;#10;13 zombies&amp;#10;6 survivors&amp;#10;2 dogs&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
